unittitle_ssm: Ed Leffingwell Jack Smith Curatorial Files
abstract_ssm: The Edward Leffingwell Jack Smith Curatorial Files include correspondence, manuscripts, clippings and audio recordings associated with Leffingwell's organization of the exhibition "Jack Smith: Flaming Creature" at P.S. 1 (New York) and associated printed matter, including material created by Jack Smith.
